  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"1.2.0-alpha01\" data-text=\"Version 1.2.0-alpha01\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.2.0-alpha01</h3>\n<p>January 12, 2022</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.compose.ui:ui-*:1.2.0-alpha01</code> is released. <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/8b1e748d80de10c087ce57eaaa93cd209cccebad..f09f3e0f47cacc65a631115deac08ee8cc132ceb/compose/ui\">Version 1.2.0-alpha01 contains these commits.</a></p>\n<p><strong>API Changes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Deprecated <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">FontFamily.canLoadSynchronously</code>. This property has\nno semantic meaning. (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/Ica5ef39f37c96a75502a1f25dff2ced62f54c019\">Ica5ef</a>)</li>\n<li>Added identity field to <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">CompositionData</code> for generating\ninvariant ids in the Layout Inspector. (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/Ic116e6682233c31ccc4a81f8cf0cc96cac4a83ca\">Ic116e</a>)</li>\n<li>Added Wear OS device ids to Preview devices list (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/I93232e4ea62f20e20d3193ee8b79c800026c01f2\">I93232</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Dependency Updates</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Now depends on Kotlin <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">1.6.10</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"version_11_2\" data-text=\"Version 1.1\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.1</h2>",
  "commitsUrl": "https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/8b1e748d80de10c087ce57eaaa93cd209cccebad..f09f3e0f47cacc65a631115deac08ee8cc132ceb/compose/ui"
}